Find the missing values of different columns (features).¶

In [13]:
null_df = df.isna().sum().sort_values(ascending=False)
null_df = null_df.reset_index(drop = False)
null_df = null_df.rename(columns={"index": "Columns", 0:"Value"})
null_df['proportion'] = (null_df['Value']/len(df))*100
